data.value: The Witch doctor of the Savannah Swamps. Bill Bourbon visited her house in the swamp 3 days prior to his murder. Mr. Bourbon had been seeing her for some months leading up to his death to recieve treatement for his cronic headaches. Nathaniel Nutmeg claims to have seen her at the local bar he owns right before the murder. The local bar is close to the Bourbon Mansion where the murder was commited, and Nathaniel recalls her to of had 'suspicious behavior' that night at the bar.
